sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor OP as Operator/Scheduler
    participant JOB as Forecast Training Job
    participant CDB as Cleansing DB
    participant SDB as Staging DB
    participant RES as In-Memory Resampler
    participant TRN as Model Trainer
    participant FS as Model Filesystem
    participant REG as Forecast Registry DB

    OP->>JOB: Start training run (batch)
    JOB->>CDB: Query MIN(bucket_start_utc) for selected cleansing run
    CDB-->>JOB: training_cutoff_utc
    JOB->>SDB: Discover exchange/symbol scope before cutoff
    SDB-->>JOB: series list

    loop each exchange/symbol series
        JOB->>SDB: Load raw rows where ts < training_cutoff_utc
        SDB-->>JOB: raw staging rows
        JOB->>RES: Resample to target cadence (e.g. 60s)
        RES-->>JOB: ephemeral training frame
        JOB->>TRN: Train Ridge + HistGBR on same frame
        TRN-->>JOB: fitted models + metrics
        JOB->>FS: Persist model artifacts (joblib)
        FS-->>JOB: artifact paths + hashes
        JOB->>REG: Persist run/model metadata + metrics
        REG-->>JOB: model registry ids
    end

    JOB-->>OP: Training summary (success/failure counts)
